        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold dark:text-white">
          Successful Track Record
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
          My experience is a testament to triumphs across diverse projects,
          spotlighting technologies and accomplishments, offering a transparent
          glimpse into my seasoned expertise.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
